results.description: Pi Studios, LLC is an independent game development company founded in 2002 in Plano, TX.  The studio relocated to Houston, TX. in 2005 and currently employs more than 130  developers.  Check them out on the web at PiStudios.com and make friends with them on their MySpace.  You can also subscribe to their Twitter feed and follow them on Facebook.
